longBusinessSummary: New England Realty Associates Limited Partnership engages in acquiring, developing, holding for investment, operating, and selling real estate properties in the United States. It owns and operates various residential apartments, condominium units, and commercial properties located in Massachusetts and New Hampshire. NewReal, Inc. serves as the general partner of the company. The company was incorporated in 1977 and is headquartered in Allston, Massachusetts.
